Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:44.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Banished to the moon for a thousand years
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:47.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But her olden traditions still fed their fears
